snippet.title: Rune of Eternity Early Access Trailer 2
snippet.description:
The open-world adventure Rune of Eternity finally has a release date!

Grab your sword and set out to explore the land of Thebryll and uncover its many secrets in search of the pieces of the sacred Eternity Rune this Halloween!

Follow the game here!
Itch: https://crookedbeaker.itch.io/rune-of-eternity
Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/roe/393665

Or follow the creator!
https://twitter.com/CrookedBeaker

Game by Crooked Beaker Games, published by Good Friend Studios.
